'''Abul Bashar''' ({{lang-bn|আবুল বাশার}}) is a popular [[Bengali language|Bengali]] writer from the state of [[West Bengal]] in [[India]]. He was born in 1951 in Hamarpur in [[Murshidabad district]]. Bashar is known for his Left-leaning stance and secularism (needs source).
