{{Expand Esperanto|Irana Esperanto-Asocio|date=February 2017}}
The '''Iranian Esperanto Association''' ({{lang-eo|Irana Esperanto-Asocio}}, '''IREA'''), founded in 1996, is the national association of the [[World Esperanto Association]] ({{lang-eo|Universala Esperanto-Asocio}})  in [[Iran]].

The core of IREA is based on the [[Iranian Esperantist Youth Organization]] ({{lang-eo|Irana Esperantista Junulara Organizo}}) and current official organ of IREA is the journal ''[[Irana Esperantisto]]''.<ref name="liberafolio">{{cite web|url=http://www.liberafolio.org/2013/unua-irana-esperanto-kongreso-okazos-en-2014|title=Unua Irana Esperanto-Kongreso okazos en 2014 &mdash; Libera Folio|publisher=liberafolio.org|accessdate=2014-01-24}}</ref><ref name="espero">{{cite web|url=http://www.espero.ir/pri-irea/|title=Pri IREA Irana Esperanto-Asocio|publisher=espero.ir|accessdate=2014-01-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201150054/http://www.espero.ir/pri-irea/|archivedate=2014-02-01|df=}}</ref><ref name="espero2">{{cite web|url=http://www.espero.com.cn/2013-11/25/content_30695525.htm|title=Unua Irana Esperanto-Kongreso okazos en 2014|publisher=espero.com.cn|accessdate=2014-04-03}}</ref>

